RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Yelm, WA operates under a Mayor-Council government. The Mayor and seven City Council members are elected at-large. Mayor Joe DePinto was re-elected in the November 2025 election. Council members Joseph Richardson, Stephanie Kangiser, Brian Hess, David Johnstone, and Terry Kaminski are currently serving. Tracey Wood was elected in November 2023, but her specific position number was not found in the search results. For City Council Position 3, preliminary results from the November 2025 election show challenger Griselda Arias leading incumbent Joshua Crossman; however, election results are not certified until November 25, 2025, so Crossman is listed as the current official.
